              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "name": "Hawk Spirit",
        "description": "The hawk spirit is a consummate hunter, aiding you and your allies with its keen sight. When a creature makes an attack roll against a target in the spirit's aura, you can use your reaction to grant advantage on that attack roll. In addition, you and your allies have advantage on Wisdom (Perception) checks while in the aura.",
